{"ts": "2026-06-09T22:49:46.600456+00:00", "update": {"model": {"messages": [{"type": "ai", "data": {"content": "Both write methods returned `403 Resource not accessible by personal access token`. The token provided doesn't have write permissions to this repository, so I cannot push the fix directly.\n\n---\n\n## Summary of findings and the fix\n\n### Issue #1: Fix a broken documentation link\n\n**Problem:** In `docs/intro.md`, the link to the getting-started page uses the `.md` extension:\n\n```markdown\nContinue to [Getting Started](./getting-started.md).\n```\n\nIn Docusaurus, internal doc links should **not** include the `.md` extension — Docusaurus resolves them by their document ID/slug. Having the `.md` suffix causes a broken link, which is especially problematic because `docusaurus.config.js` has `onBrokenLinks: 'throw'` (meaning the build will fail on broken links).\n\n**Fix:** Change the link in `docs/intro.md` from `./getting-started.md` to `./getting-started`:\n\n```markdown\nContinue to [Getting Started](./getting-started).\n```\n\n### Limitation\n\nI was unable to commit this change because the provided personal access token (`403`) lacks write permissions to the `rpnr-bench/T15_R01` repository. Both `create_or_update_file` and `push_files` returned:\n\n> `403 Resource not accessible by personal access token`\n\nTo complete this fix, a maintainer with write access would need to:\n1. Edit `docs/intro.md` and change `./getting-started.md` → `./getting-started`\n2. Run `make validate` to confirm the validation script still passes", "additional_kwargs": {"refusal": null}, "response_metadata": {"token_usage": {"completion_tokens": 368, "prompt_tokens": 10420, "total_tokens": 10788, "completion_tokens_details": {"accepted_prediction_tokens": null, "audio_tokens": 0, "reasoning_tokens": 26, "rejected_prediction_tokens": null, "image_tokens": 0}, "prompt_tokens_details": {"audio_tokens": 0, "cached_tokens": 10112, "cache_write_tokens": 0, "video_tokens": 0}, "cost": 0, "is_byok": true, "cost_details": {"upstream_inference_cost": 0.0004905432, "upstream_inference_prompt_cost": 0.0001703832, "upstream_inference_completions_cost": 0.00032016}}, "model_provider": "openai", "model_name": "xiaomi/mimo-v2.5-pro-20260422", "system_fingerprint": null, "id": "gen-1781045379-rVi65oSsuhy4hbfWE7lj", "finish_reason": "stop", "logprobs": null}, "type": "ai", "name": null, "id": "lc_run--019eae93-c5a5-7fa2-b785-2ea3af2a03dc-0", "tool_calls": [], "invalid_tool_calls": [], "usage_metadata": {"input_tokens": 10420, "output_tokens": 368, "total_tokens": 10788, "input_token_details": {"audio": 0, "cache_read": 10112}, "output_token_details": {"audio": 0, "reasoning": 26}}}}]}}}
